dc_title_s: Roads and ROW: Waupaca County, Wisconsin, 2019
dct_alternativeTitle_sm: Roads and ROW Waupaca County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2019.For Roads: [This data represents the Waupaca County transportation network. A single line is used to represent the center of a road. All roads are geocoded with a address range.]For ROW: [The road right-of-way(ROW) layer for Waupaca County includes county, state, and U.S. highways, town roads, city streets and alleys. The Road ROW layer is available in a county-wide or individual layer for each township, city, or village. The road ROW polygons were derived from various sources. These sources include, but are not limited to, deeds, surveys, subdivision plats, highway plats, Town records, and State records.]
